title: 8 Chess Books on Openings (gnv64)
description:
A collection of 8 chess books on opening theory in PDF format:

1. Chess Opening Essentials Volume 4 - 1.c4/Nf3/Minor Systems by Stefan Diuric, Dimitri Komarov, Claudio pantaleoni
2. Easy Guide to the Classical Sicilian by GM Jouni Yrjola
3. Improve Your Opening Play by Chris Ward
4. Play the Nimzo-Indian Defence by GN Svetozar Gligoric
5. Starting Out - Alekhine's Defence by John Cox
6. Starting Out - The Grunfeld Defence by Jakob Aagaard
7. The Bb5 Sicilian by Richard Palliser
8. The Two Knights Defence by Jan Pinsky
